attributes.part.0.content:
#cloud-config
---
output: { all: "| tee -a /var/log/cloud-init-output.log" }
runcmd:
  - aws s3api get-object --bucket cna-624a2139-us-east-1 --key zero-downtime.gif /usr/share/nginx/site/html/cna/zero-downtime.gif
  - sudo amazon-linux-extras install nginx1.12
  - sudo systemctl enable nginx
  - sudo systemctl start nginx
write_files:
  - encoding: b64
    content: 
    path: /etc/pki/nginx/server.crt
  - encoding: b64
    content: 
    path: /etc/pki/nginx/private/server.key
  - encoding: b64
    content: 
    path: /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
  - encoding: b64
    content: 
    path: /usr/share/nginx/site/html/cna/index.html
  - content: |
      {
        "status" : "UP"
      }
    path: /usr/share/nginx/site/html/cna/health
